headline.print_headline: Renicks Sisters Secure Scotland's First Golds
headline.main: Renicks Sisters Secure Scotland's First Golds

lead_paragraph: Scottish sisters Kimberley and Louise Renicks landed the host nation's first gold medals of the Commonwealth Games by claiming judo victories an hour apart on Thursday.
